Automatic dependency install script (.NET Core 2.1):
```
wget https://dot.net/v1/dotnet-install.sh
./dotnet-install.sh -c Current
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Ubuntu distributions require the following libraries installed:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
```
liblttng-ust0
libcurl3 (for 14.x and 16.x)
libcurl4 (for 18.x)
libssl1.0.0
libkrb5-3
zlib1g
libicu52 (for 14.x)
libicu55 (for 16.x)
libicu57 (for 17.x)
libicu60 (for 18.x)
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CentOS and Fedora distributions require the following libraries installed:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
```
lttng-ust
libcurl
openssl-libs
krb5-libs
libicu
zlib
Fedora users: If your openssl's version >= 1.1, you'll need to install compat-openssl10.
```